novell <novl> sets two for one stock split
    santa clara, calif., march 11 - 
novell inc said its board declared a two-for-one stock split, payable
to holders of record at the close of business on march 31. it said
shareholders at the annual meeting approved a doubling of authorized
common shares to 30 mln from 15 mln and a limitation of directors'
liability. reuter 
